                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="text-center p-3 border rounded">
                    <i class="bi bi-scooter text-warning" style="font-size: 2.5rem;"></i>
                    <h5 class="mt-3 mb-3">Xe Máy</h5>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-2">
                        <span>Vé Ngày:</span>
